replies.body:
Well, same story for her: {{champion:164}} 
Everything about her and the way they teased her just screamed assassin. Was really disturbed to see that she is actually a diver. xD

Nevertheless, Nocturne's playstyle is that of a diver. He has to build some defences, since he has (unlike an assassin) no reliable escape if he is in the middle of a fight. If he goes in, he has to commit and survive.
